Usage: define_add_on_module_model [-help] [-commit_callback <string>]
                                  -type <string> {[-create_callback <string>] [-set_callback <string>] [-restore_callback <string>] [-write_context_callback <string>]}

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-commit_callback <string>            # <commit callback> proc commit_call_back
                                     # {dir cell tag args} (string, optional)
-create_callback <string>            # <crate_module_model callback> proc
                                     # create_call_back {dir cell tag args}
                                     # (string, optional)
-restore_callback <string>           # <restore_module_model callback> proc
                                     # restore_call_back {dir cell tag args}
                                     # (string, optional)
-set_callback <string>               # <set_module_model callback> proc
                                     # set_call_back {dir cell tag args}
                                     # (string, optional)
-type <string>                       # <type of add_on module model>
                                     # (string, required)
-write_context_callback <string>     # <write_module_model_context callback>
                                     # proc write_context_call_back {dir cell
                                     # tag args} (string, optional)